The teak armour case can be built in the armour case space of the costume room in a player-owned house. It requires 64 Construction to upgrade the oak armour case and when built, it gives 270 experience. The player must have a hammer and a saw in their inventory to build it.

The teak armour case can hold 50 sets of armour listed below.

Note: Attempting to remove the armour case with sets of armour instead will alert the player to remove everything before the action can be completed.
